      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Wow! You collected everything...!!! Great! Okay then, I will give the #b#t4031064##k back as I promised. Hmm... I liked this cape a lot... Well... promise is a promise... Take it...!"
