      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Wow! You got them all! Okay. Now I can just give these to #p401# and get the claw. Oh yeah, I will give you something good, since my mom gave me something to use only when I really need it. It will be a lot of help for you."
      },
